name: Wonderful Whiskers
description:
Movember (https://movember.com) is an annual event to raise funds to make a difference for mental health, suicide prevention, prostate cancer and testicular cancer.


Proceeds from all sales of this piece will be donated to Movember.


Controls:
n or swipe up - toggle visibility of the nose
c or swipe down - toggle ‘realistic’ facial hair colours
m or swipe left or right - create a new nose and facial hair combination
